Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Freestanding commercial property in the heart of Woodbridge. Excellent street exposure and frontage on Kipling Avenue. Ample parking at the back with up to 16 stalls. Suitable for many office and retail uses such as law, accounting, dentist etc. First floor open concept with second floor offices and basement storage.
